<subSubSection id="0FE0BF6590F146393E72BFD02F930BEE" pageNumber="301" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="686254884239861D8C8118655A07EB2D" pageNumber="301">
<emphasis id="1705B25BCD626D6AAA32C3589062F474" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Note:</emphasis>
There has been considerable confusion over the type choice for 
<emphasis id="85E5ED78090DF3D8AFB5D2CE5FA20B46" italics="true" pageNumber="301">
<taxonomicName id="B992950424CEBDB9096DE5D46829FB93" authority="Linnaeus, 1753" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Antholyza</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
The earlier choice (Hitchcock in 
<emphasis id="C99E35AFDE41067744478A25A64B43AB" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Amer. J. Bot.</emphasis>
10: 514. 1923; 
<emphasis id="6F823780B32920FE007E24E8D4594850" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Prop. Brit. Bot.</emphasis>
: 118. 1929) is of 
<taxonomicName id="679921EEC5D711B3B79E15F5566B5E25" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cunonia">
<emphasis id="64FC8BB1E1850F90967E3956F57D862E" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Anth. cunonia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(now recognised as a species of 
<taxonomicName id="7E69A61C6FC9E6EDEDC70CA678914FD1" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Gladiolus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CB91A89B668CA07B1899987D8D8984FB" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Gladiolus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) into which 
<taxonomicName id="DD8AA8C370A34BB33A7C7503B7902AD3" authority="Linnaeus, 1753" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="C934EFE5304DA6D3772AE97AA92DC0D7" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Antholyza</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
falls as a synonym. However, if 
<taxonomicName id="3A69361FECAE5A5CC4D600EE403D8072" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cunonia">
<emphasis id="E8D742C52ABF3006D6CBC071E762AEF5" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Anth. cunonia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is treated as the 
<typeStatus id="4C5D94743CE08336C825DD349C382D92">generitype</typeStatus>
, but as 
<taxonomicName id="7080E2D074DAD699288E91FC6F56328F" authority="(L.) R. Br." authorityName="R. Br." authorityYear="1932" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Anomalesia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cunonia">
<emphasis id="6B70FE07750F37BCB02D9D25AA305440" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Anomalesia cunonia</emphasis>
(L.) R. Br.
</taxonomicName>
, the latter genus would be displaced by 
<emphasis id="FDEB5E72F5EF769FC32910730F9BFA1F" italics="true" pageNumber="301">
<taxonomicName id="0E0D9737330315E754A5A811DB3294BF" authority="Linnaeus, 1753" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Antholyza</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
A later choice is 
<taxonomicName id="3E16B7DFBE63268EFC3D0396A598153E" authority="Linnaeus, 1753" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ringens">
<emphasis id="A4AD153DDBDE21EBC6D342F6CDF91AEE" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Anth. ringens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(by Brown in 
<emphasis id="51A443BC74AF92D768B33A9D90F894D6" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Trans. Roy. Soc. S. Africa</emphasis>
20: 266. 1932), sometimes accepted in this genus but more recently (Goldblatt in 
<emphasis id="86122C782DDCD6389D628810FEFD8EFD" italics="true" pageNumber="301">S. African J. Bot.</emphasis>
56: 580. 1990) transferred to 
<taxonomicName id="CFA099ACB721DF4B943CA3270B978B17" authority="Ker Gawl. Goldblatt" authorityName="Ker Gawl. Goldblatt" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Babiana" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="9588A7447D5315F37D29780820C84253" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Babiana</emphasis>
Ker Gawl. Goldblatt
</taxonomicName>
does not accept 
<taxonomicName id="1B023750FC7191E4C7B37964F54CD880" authority="Linnaeus, 1753" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ringens">
<emphasis id="9BBDCD17E8D0A71EE77680107F720469" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Anth. ringens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as the 
<typeStatus id="73B23F457B7876BB2809F3E6DB40A327">generitype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="F70D208DB0B476F4285B75675E509737" authority="Linnaeus, 1753" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="FB3D5FC25FFD48E1F0296155EF31881A" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Antholyza</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
so there is no disruption. However, 
<emphasis id="471828AEA3DCC97AAA21676AA77B44EF" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Index Nominum Genericorum</emphasis>
(ING), noting 
<normalizedToken id="7817804008BB700C2A2D7613E0740D4E" originalValue="Linnaeusâ">Linnaeus'</normalizedToken>
comments in 1753 that 
<taxonomicName id="9A9E177253810EDFCD287C5951360B5C" authority="Linnaeus, 1753" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cunonia">
<emphasis id="CE05E9528442D7FD3A8D3C2EFB735B85" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Anth. cunonia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
probably belongs to a genus distinct from 
<taxonomicName id="94CD5176E6E51E569B013AC18EA0EAFB" authority="Linnaeus, 1753" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="99B47F0A525942A040CF0543BFB81A74" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Antholyza</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, argues that it conflicts with the generic protologue, and accepts 
<taxonomicName id="E5808C75AE1AADA8F1EA0338ADDFDEC5" authority="Linnaeus, 1753" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ringens">
<emphasis id="99348B6F057B42B68714E2B32D037C57" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Anth. ringens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as 
<typeStatus id="1B4F16110A2AD725EC09EDAFB06C9C81">generitype</typeStatus>
. If this is accepted, and 
<taxonomicName id="3157C0AD06759E86B1D0DFDA1555812E" authority="Linnaeus, 1753" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ringens">
<emphasis id="D9A8496B35D8C0BC9FE671BBD9319511" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Anth. ringens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is treated as a species of 
<emphasis id="24B636A13EB6ABF68D48A9E03291E96E" italics="true" pageNumber="301">
<taxonomicName id="3939509C2834B2203688C74FF7D908B0" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Babiana" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Babiana</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="63442813B456F67073366C4A9A6B5DF5" authority="Linnaeus, 1753" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Antholyza" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Antholyza</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
becomes the correct name for 
<taxonomicName id="69FE352BE4972C12D311A814FC6FEA27" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Babiana" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="186FDFE890469A95CE3A45B0C3B019A8" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Babiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(as the latter is conserved only against 
<taxonomicName id="E99825A5560657FC304476420459B283" authority="Adans. 1763" authorityName="Adans." authorityYear="1763" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Beverna" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="D08D6EE5774DE86C37AAEBEA67EA1C85" italics="true" pageNumber="301">Beverna</emphasis>
Adans. 1763
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
